==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Uncivilized
<hw>Un*civ"i*lized</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not
civilized; not reclaimed from savage life; rude; barbarous; savage;
<as>as, the <ex>uncivilized</ex> inhabitants of Central
Africa</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not civil; coarse; clownish.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>
<rj><au>Addison.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Uncivilty</ent>⟦br⟧
